; Regression test for issue #1134: There is no --format-* option for xact (BZ#1134)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1134
;
; The xact (entry) command should respect --format like other commands do,
; but currently --format is silently ignored by xact.

2024/01/01 Payee
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test xact --format '%D %P\n' 2024/02/01 Payee 20
2024/02/01 Payee
    Expenses:Food                             $20.00
    Assets:Cash
end test
